  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/Resource">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <rdfs:label>Resource</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">General resource record of the Communication Device kind from the logistics park. It is a managed entity that can be either Physical or Virtual.

Alignment:
- *SEAS*: Whenever a Resource individual is an assembly of other resources (e.g. a server rack) or is part of an assembly (e.g. a server blade), the Resource individual can also be declared as a `seas:System` in order to benefit of the `seas:subSystemOf` relation.
  For example, Resources may be grouped in some `noria:Service` class for providing both an end-to-end analysis of the data path (i.e. Communication Devices + Connections) and an abstract object linked to some end user (e.g. Customer).
- *BOT*: A `noria:Resource` is a sub-class of `bot:Element` for setting instances in the context of a physical environment (e.g. in a building).
- *SLOGERT*: A `noria:Resource` is equivalent to a `log:Host`.
- *UCO*: A `noria:Resource` is equivalent to an UCO's observable `Device`.
</rdfs:comment>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="en">ICT resource.</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="fr">Elément structurant informatique et télécoms.</skos:altLabel>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/StructuralElement"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/seas/System"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/seas/CommunicationDevice"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/bot#Element"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://unifiedcyberontology.org/ontology/uco/observable#Device"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/sepses/ns/log#Host"/>
    <vs:term_status>stable</vs:term_status>
    <skos:changeNote>Changes in v0.2:
- Adding rdfs:subClassOf bot:Element.
- Adding rdfs:subClassOf observable:Device.
- Adding rdfs:subClassOf log:Host.
</skos:changeNote>
    <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/logOriginatingManagedObject">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty"/>
    <rdfs:label>logOriginatingManagedObject</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">The Managed Object entity at the origin of the Log record. This includes information about the service provider associated with the service request that caused a security alarm.</rdfs:comment>
    <skos:example xml:lang="en">A named Resource, Application, Security Alarm Detector, etc.</skos:example>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/EventRecord"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/Resource"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/Application"/>
    <vs:term_status>stable</vs:term_status>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/eventRelatedElement"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAttributedTo"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/pep/madeBy"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://IBCNServices.github.io/Folio-Ontology/Folio.owl#happenedAt"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/sepses/ns/log#hasSourceHost"/>
    <skos:changeNote>Changes in v0.2:
- Adding rdfs:subPropertyOf dcterms:creator.
- Adding rdfs:subPropertyOf prov:wasAttributedTo.
- Adding rdfs:subPropertyOf folio:happenedAt.
- Adding rdfs:subPropertyOf log:hasSourceHost.
- Adding reference to ITU-T X721 SecurityAlarmDetector.
- Adding reference to ITU-T X721 serviceProvider.
- Merging the noria:serviceProvider.
</skos:changeNote>
    <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://www.itu.int/rec/T-REC-X.733-199202-I/"/>
    <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://www.itu.int/ITU-T/formal-language/itu-t/x/x721/1992/x721.html#-managedObjectInstance"/>
    <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://www.itu.int/ITU-T/formal-language/itu-t/x/x721/1992/x721.html#-SecurityAlarmDetector"/>
